window.bookSummaryJSON = "<p><b>After surviving the attack on Coral Bay, Liv Brodbeck's most deadly secret is in danger of being exposed.</b></p> <p>To protect her, Archmagus Jurian sends Liv, Wren, and Arjun with a group of Journeymen to the fortress-city of Akela Kila, in Arjun's homeland of Lendh ka Dakruim. The Well of Bones, grave of the Vædic Lady Costia, is erupting, spewing forth an endless tide of re-animated corpses, and Liv will need to use everything she's learned to survive.</p> <p>But the true danger waits for her back at Coral Bay, where the future of the Mages Guild is thrown into turmoil by the new monarch of Lucania...</p>"; 
